’ђђЩіTitle: title: hide-env
Path: Examples
Content:
Hide an environment variable.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> $env.HZ_ENV_ABC = 1; hide-env HZ_ENV_ABC; 'HZ_ENV_ABC' in $env
false

```
